title: DECEMBER BRIDE -- The Budget ( 2nd Season )
description:
Midway through the second year, this is one of the first episodes to have a more modern set. It looks like the family sold their house and moved into a sleek apartment.  It's this cool set and furniture that were used until the end of the series after 5 years in 1959.

The Danny Thomas Show change their set design a few times, with no explanation ever given in the show itself
